Did a set of 5 plates before this hoping it would feel light weight baby, but it was definitely heavy weight daddy so decided to torture myself with some high volume squats immediately after💀

🚨ALSO got something really exciting coming up, me and @melissabum are going to be having a transformation contest. With most peoples gyms opening back up it’s the perfect time to start some good habits and get back in shape or into your best shape.
You’ll be getting nutrition and training plans as well as check ins from either myself or Melissa to guide you through the process. We’re going to make it a fun sibling rivalry of team MelBum vs team Cbum with prizes for the best transformation.
With myself starting prep in a few weeks as well it’ll be like you guys are prepping with me.
I’ll have a lot more info to come at the beginning of next week so if your interested keep an eye out for the announcement👀

node.text:
Can’t believe I finally get to share this news with you guys... I am officially the newest co-owner of @getrawnutrition
This is it, this is the end game.
Stepping away from being an athlete of someone else’s brand and actually getting to help and decide what goes in and comes out of the business.
I have always tried my best to stay connected with you guys who have supported my journey so much and this will be no different. I believe I have a unique perspective of what you guys want and what I would want out of a brand giving me the opportunity to help build something really special here.
I felt perfectly aligned coming to this decision to join @d_iacovone and @mattjansen8 as it was clear their intentions were to build more of a culture than a business and we are going to do just that.
So huge thank you to those two gentleman for giving me this opportunity and trusting in me.
Transitioning into a business owner and putting my personal vision into a brand has always been a goal of mine. I go more in depth in my YouTube video I just posted (link in my bio), but for now I am just really grateful and beyond excited for this opportunity. 
We have so many exciting announcements rolling out soon and I’m so grateful for your guys continued support as you are the reason I get opportunities like this that I want to make sure you are all going to love what’s coming as much as myself.
So stay tuned and as always use code CBUM 😉

node.text:
The sad part of opening new doors is sometimes you need to close some good ones behind you.
Bittersweet news today, and to get right to the bitter part is I am going to be parting ways with @jacked_factory
It’s truly been an amazing couple years and I’m so grateful to have been apart of the brand.
From what they stand for and the team behind the scenes, it’s been a great experience that I honestly didn’t see myself leaving for some time.
I wouldn’t be leaving if it were for just another sponsorship, I’ll announce the sweet part of this news next week explaining how this is a whole new venture I’m departing on.
But for now this is just a farewell to JF remembering the good times we had.
I also just posted a YouTube video going into more detail about all this, click the link in my bio to check that out🙏🏼
